Patch Set 2:

@Sabari

There are two ways to include additional namespaces.  I can add them as a subsequent section to the page, .e.g. after the options in the glance-api.conf section, then provide a paragraph of additional libraries, and then provide the options.  (This requires no changes to how show-options works).

The alternative is to try and embed the additional namespaces.  This introduces two complexities, first its a code change, but second it makes the ordering of options difficult. A test shows that the DEFAULT section starts with all the logging options, rather than the more import Glance DEFAULT options.

I will provide a patchset of the first option so you can see what it looks like.
Uploaded patch set 3.
